```plantuml
@startuml oovk_dataengg-covid19-aws

actor User

participant "Jupyter Notebook" as Notebook
participant "AWS Open Data" as OpenData
participant "AWS S3" as S3
participant "AWS Athena" as Athena
participant "Pandas DataFrame" as DataFrame
participant "AWS Redshift" as Redshift

User -> Notebook: Start ETL Process

Notebook -> OpenData: Query and retrieve datasets
OpenData -> Notebook: Return datasets

Notebook -> Athena: Execute queries on datasets
Athena -> Notebook: Return query results

Notebook -> DataFrame: Load data into Pandas DataFrames

DataFrame -> DataFrame: Transform data (wrangling, merging, feature engineering)

DataFrame -> S3: Save transformed data as CSV to S3

Notebook -> Redshift: Connect to Redshift

Notebook -> Redshift: Execute SQL CREATE TABLE statements
Redshift -> Notebook: Tables created in Redshift

User -> Notebook: Verify data in Redshift

@enduml
```